{
  "stem": "3360.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this was-- I was 11 years old, so it was 1935.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so that was two years into the Nazi government.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So this Walter Burgerman, whom he was seeing very, very rarely at that point in time, and who was not there, rang the bell in his Hitler Youth uniform, in his Hitler Youth uniform, which you know was a swastika on the arm and a brown shirt and the triangle, the tie.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he wanted to congratulate my cousin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I see him there-- as I'm sitting here today-- I see him reaching out his hand to my cousin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[SOBS] And he's wanted to congratulate him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was a stranger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was the strangest, the strangest situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the kid-- he was a kid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, what did he know about hating this particular person, because he was a Jew?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this is one of the things that I feel that is kind of significant to know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That just because they were Germans, they weren't all immediately converted to this way of thinking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They knew that they weren't to associate with Jewish Germans anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there he was, he came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was another-- there was another little innocent situation when I was still in my first four years of school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was one girl with whom I was friendly who lived not far from us who went-- who was in the Hitler Youth at an early age.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of them went in there, because these were-- these were children-- these were only children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were a lot of only-- only children, because the economy was so bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had no brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had no brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
